<HEADLINE>
TREASURY SET TO AUCTION BILLS AND NOTES
</HEADLINE>
   (mk) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Treasury's schedule of financing this week offers Monday's
regular weekly auction of new three- and six-month bills and
auctions of 5-year and 10-year notes on Wednesday.
</P>
